SELECT max (ingested_datetime)  FROM [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[sb_s51_advice_tmp] order by 1
SELECT max (ingestiondate) FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[sb_s51_advice] 

select count(*) FROM [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[sb_s51_advice]
select count(*) FROM [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[sb_s51_advice] where message_type is not null and message_type != 'Delete' and cast(ingested_datetime as date) <= '2024-06-17'
select count(*) FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[sb_s51_advice]
select count(*) FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[sb_s51_advice] where isactive='Y'
select count(*) FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[nsip_s51_advice] where isactive='Y'
select top 10 * FROM [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[sb_s51_advice] order by adviceid
